short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tools and custom features for Bluesky website, bsky.app

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An extension which provides tools and extra features on Bluesky web app, https://bsky.app. This extension currently focuses on enabling bookmarks on Bluesky, implemented similar to the 'other' social app. More features to be added soon.

This extension identify users by did:plc to save bookmarks. Users may choose to keep bookmarks on the official server or on a third-party server, or even host their own server to manage their bookmarks. 

Official repositories at https://github.com/biskuvi. For feature requests, feedback, bugs, help or enquiries, contact https://bsky.app/profile/bskv.site or visit Bluesky API Touchers Discord server.
